data.description: This sprawling 2-story home boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and a home office that could be utilized as a 5th bedroom. Situated on a spacious lot, this residence invites you to unwind on the screened-in patio or roam freely in the expansive fenced yard. The attached 2-car garage ensures both convenience and ample storage. If you're yearning for a taste of rustic charm coupled with modern comfort, look no further – this property is your storybook dreams realized.
